<taxonomicName id="B8B24D2FFB5CFFB0EA2FFC4F2068A1A3" box="[1029,1150,913,937]" pageId="11" pageNumber="11" rank="tribe" tribe="Calliopsini">Calliopsini</taxonomicName>
were last revised by 
<bibRefCitation id="1B234B5DFB5CFFB0ED75FC6D27F6A1C0" author="Ruz, L." box="[863,992,946,970]" pageId="11" pageNumber="11" pagination="209 - 256" refId="ref46555" refString="Ruz, L. 1991. Classification and phylogenetic relationships of the panurgine bees: the Calliopsini and allies (Hymenoptera: Andrenidae). University of Kansas Science Bulletin 54 (7): 209 - 256." type="journal article" year="1991">Ruz (1991)</bibRefCitation>
