<bibRefCitation id="1B234B5DFB5CFFB0EC86FC0D204DA1E1" author="Roig-Alsina, A. &amp; L. A. Compagnucci" box="[684,1115,979,1003]" pageId="11" pageNumber="11" pagination="99 - 112" refId="ref46315" refString="Roig-Alsina, A., and L. A. Compagnucci. 2003. Description, phylogenetic relationships, and biology of Litocalliopsis adesmiae, a new genus and species of South American calliopsine bees (Hymenoptera, Andrenidae). Revista del Museo Argentino de Ciencias Naturales 5 (1): 99 - 112." type="journal article" year="2003">Roig-Alsina and Compagnucci (2003)</bibRefCitation>
